From 329ac1edb8085898a5bce5fe1a5d1ab2b74547a6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Juan Manuel Lopez Carrillo <juanmanuellopezcarrillo@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 02:00:34 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 092/131] config: activar SUN55I_A523_CPU_CCU
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

El CCU de CPU del A523 va built-in (=y) para estar disponible pronto en el
arranque (prerequisito de cpufreq). olddefconfig, una sola opción nueva.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 .config | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/.config b/.config
index 3e11d8dae..da4e2b24d 100644
--- a/.config
+++ b/.config
@@ -7165,6 +7165,7 @@ CONFIG_SUN50I_H6_CCU=y
 CONFIG_SUN50I_H616_CCU=y
 CONFIG_SUN50I_H6_R_CCU=y
 CONFIG_SUN55I_A523_CCU=y
+CONFIG_SUN55I_A523_CPU_CCU=y
 CONFIG_SUN55I_A523_MCU_CCU=y
 CONFIG_SUN55I_A523_R_CCU=y
 CONFIG_SUN6I_RTC_CCU=y
